snippet.title: Pokemon Legends Z-A - Nintendo Switch 2 Edition Trailer | Nintendo Direct
snippet.description:
Pokemon Legends Z-A will come with enhanced resolution and framerate when played on the Nintendo Switch 2 as opposed to the Nintendo Switch with the Nintendo Switch 2 Edition of the game.

#IGN #NintendoSwitch2
